description: Our hero Dan Morgenstern speaks fondly of the great pianist, singer, and composer Jimmy Rowles -- as an accompanist and soloist -- in this interview at his home last year.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).  Interrupted by Dan's cellphone, but we return for Part Two.
